            </svg>
          </span>
        </h3>
        <h3 class="my-2">
          <span>
            砂岩
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="-mt-0.5 h-5 w-6 inline" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
